<TabItem value="scoop">

**The classic way to install binaries on Windows is to use [Scoop][urls.scoop].**

<Steps headingDepth={3}>

1.  ### Add Qovery bucket
    ```bash
    scoop bucket add qovery https://github.com/Qovery/scoop-qovery-cli
    ```
2.  ### Install the CLI
    ```bash
    scoop install qovery-cli
    ```

</Steps>

</TabItem>

